    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package for submission despite multiple factor gaps, on the basis that Monte Carlo UQ bounds were conservative and the partial validation evidence was judged sufficient for a conditional regulatory filing. NOTE: This acceptance is erroneous with respect to the model version in effect — the ValidationResults supporting this decision were generated under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-15-build-2024-q3-build-2 (modelVersion 2024-q3-build-2), whereas the UofA declares currentModelVersion 2026-q1-build-7. The 2026-Q1 rebuild introduced revised hemolysis model coefficients and updated near-wall treatment; no revalidation has been performed under the current model version. The supporting evidence therefore does not apply to the model of record.",
